      "date": "2018-05-03 18:12:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nAs mentioned in the review of https://review.whamcloud.com/30980\n\n    Note that 0x4 and 0x20 are already used, please use 0x10 for this.\n\nIt also mentions in the code there:\n\n * update obd_connect_names[] for lprocfs_rd_connect_flags(), add the\n * flag to check_obd_connect_data(), and updates wiretests accordingly, so it\n * can be approved and landed easily to reserve the flag for future use. */",
