      "date": "2018-05-04 02:52:40.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n> Oleg, when will the patch \"LU-4684 ptlrpc: add dir migration\n > connect flag\" be merged, please? I hope very soon? I would like to\n > either 1) wait until that patch is merged or 2) rebase this patch\n > to latest master branch now. Otherwise, I will need to rebase patch\n > of \"LU-10472 osc: add T10PI support for RPC checksum\" for multiple\n > times because of dependency problems. If merging of \"LU-4684\n > ptlrpc: add dir migration connect flag\" won't happen in a few\n > hours, maybe I should rebase this patch to latest master branch.\n\nLU-4684 patch will be merged in the next couple of days. So if you don't base on top of it you'll need to rebase once the merge actually happens.",
